wixl-heat(1)                                                                         General Commands Manual                                                                         wixl-heat(1)

NNAAMMEE
       wixl-heat - builds Wix XML fragments from a list of files and directories

SSYYNNOOPPSSIISS
       wwiixxll--hheeaatt [<_o_p_t_i_o_n> [<_o_p_t_i_o_n> ...]]

DDEESSCCRRIIPPTTIIOONN
       wwiixxll--hheeaatt builds an Wix XML fragment from a list of files given on the standard input. The XML fragment is output to the standard output.

OOPPTTIIOONNSS
       --hh, ----hheellpp
              Print a help message and exit.

       ----ddiirreeccttoorryy--rreeff <_d_i_r_e_c_t_o_r_y>
              Specifies the directory reference for the DDiirreeccttoorryyRReeff element.

       ----ccoommppoonneenntt--ggrroouupp <_c_o_m_p_o_n_e_n_t _g_r_o_u_p>
              Specifies the component group for the CCoommppoonneennttGGrroouupp element.

       ----vvaarr <<_v_a_r_i_a_b_l_e>>
              Specifies the variable to use for the source directory in the SSoouurrccee attribute of the FFiillee elements.

       --pp, ----pprreeffiixx <_d_i_r_e_c_t_o_r_y>
              Specifies the prefix in which the files are based (this is removed from the resulting file names).

       --xx, ----eexxcclluuddee <_d_i_r_e_c_t_o_r_y>
              Excludes any files with the given prefix.

